A suburb of neighboring metropolous, Detroit, it has a population slightly less than 100,000. Home of Henry Ford of automotive fame, it features [http://www.hfmgv.org/ The Henry Ford], a complex consisting of The Henry Ford Museum, Greenfield Village and an IMAX Theater. Also found are the [http://www.henryfordestate.org/ Henry Ford Estate] and the newly built [http://www.dearbornfordcenter.com/ Ford Community & Performing Arts Center].